            <h3>Font Family</h3>
        <p>Brandon Grotesque is used throughout the app. Its rounded corners and low contrast add a sense of
            friendliness. Since it is sans serif, it&#39;s much more legible on screens rather than print. The geometric
            face adds a feeling of helpful instruction for people to latch onto.</p>
