            <h3>Iconography</h3>
        <p>TikTok’s icons are taken from SF Symbols so that they are native to iOS apps. Flat illustrations add a
            playful and cheerful feel to TikTok, and, once tapped/ activated, those illustrations play an animation
            on-screen.</p>
